{
  "id": "adv_card_ktn_06_01",
  "title": "長瀬琴乃 1話 どんな想いも燃料に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――NEXT VENUSグランプリ歴代優勝者達の",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――It's been a while since our participation in the",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "祭典への出演が決まってしばらく経った頃",
      "translations": {
        "en": "NEXT VENUS Grand Prix was confirmed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "忙しいのに付き合ってもらってすみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry for making you accompany me while you're busy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3666666943,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫だよ。それに、最近はあまり\nゆっくり話せてなかったしな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay.\nBesides‚ we haven't had much time to talk lately.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.9333333412,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.2310887295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます\nそれで、相談なんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you.\nSo‚ I have something I want to discuss.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.4977553962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.3310882209
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "サニピとの合同練習に……集中出来ないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't focus during joint practices with Sunny Peace.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.3310882209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.7310886024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピがBIG4になってから、月ストとの差が\n開いていってる気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since they became part of the BIG4‚\nit feels like the gap between us and Moon Tempest is widening.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.9977552691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達も頑張ってるんですけど\nサニピは仕事の幅がどんどん広がっていて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're doing our best‚\nbut Sunny Peace's work is expanding rapidly‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.7644213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.9644207913
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "「月ストに比べてサニピは絶好調」っていう風に\n世間でも思われてるんだと……肌で感じるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and they are seen as being in excellent shape.\nEven in public… I can feel it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.5977541247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.564420537
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "周りの意見は気にしなくていい……と言いたいけど\n実際は難しいよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's easy to say not to care about others' opinions‚\nbut in reality‚ it's challenging.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.2333344856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "リーダーとして月ストをうまく引っ張れなくて\nこんな風に思われてるのが悔しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As the leader‚ I'm frustrated that\nMoon Tempest is seen this way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7171868601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.0505229908
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "私、祭典に出ること自体はとても嬉しいんです\nサニピと出演することも、お姉ちゃんの曲を歌うことも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm thrilled to be performing at the festival.\nSinging alongside Sunny Peace and singing my sister's song…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.4171896575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.8171891489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "でも、サニピと一緒に練習をすると、同じように歌って\n踊っていても、持ってる空気感が違う気がするんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But when I practice with Sunny Peace‚\neven if we sing and dance similarly‚ there's a different vibe.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.2838558155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.5171881316
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "分かるよ。勢いに乗ってる時とそうでない時とでは\nまとう雰囲気が変わると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand. The aura you exude can change depending on\nwhether you're in the groove or not.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.4000024238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、今自分は、さくら達みたいに輝けてないんだな\nって思うと、悔しくて練習に集中出来なくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now‚ I feel like I'm not shining like Sakura-chan and the others.\nIt's frustrating‚ and I can't concentrate on practice in this state.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.722931953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.4562642691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "こんな状態でお姉ちゃんの曲を歌うなんて\nお姉ちゃんに……申し訳ないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Singing my sister's song under these conditions…\nI feel sorry for her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.4229309358,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 98.8895950593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい、こんなことを話しても\nどうしようもないとは分かってるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for talking about this‚\neven though I know it's not something I can change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.1895950593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃がこんな風に悩みを打ち明けてくれたことが\n俺は嬉しいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad Kotono shared your worries\nwith me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666706162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.4107262887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.4107262887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "最近、無理して笑ったり、いつも通り\n振る舞おうとしてただろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Lately‚ you've been forcing yourself to smile\nand act like nothing's wrong‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.566669599,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "こうして琴乃から相談してもらってなかったら\n俺から切り出そうとしてたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you hadn't come to me‚\nI would have approached you about it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.2333362656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.5222221014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは……本当によく\n私達を見てくれてますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ you really…\nYou pay close attention to us‚ don't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7555554347,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.6222221014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺は琴乃達のマネージャーだからな。それにしても\nこの悩みは、月ストやサニピのみんなには言えないよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm Moon Tempest's manager‚ after all. Nonetheless‚\nthis worry is something you can't discuss with the others.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.000001915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "はい……なんていうか、月ストやサニピの\nみんなには、近いからこそ言えなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ it's… because we're close to\nMoon Tempest and Sunny Peace‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.2189566888,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.0522900221
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "特に……さくらには",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and especially Sakura-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0522900221,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 146.2522951083
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01/sud_vo_adv_card_ktn_06_01-ktn017.m4a",
